comments.body: Quote from: Al-Qisaer on August 09, 2023, 08:06:16 AMSorry my friend for your feeling but I'm asking and I'm new its worth in my Trust wallet around 300B Can you add the name of the token or exchange? Some scam exchanges perform double scam, where give you the price of the token worth thousands of dollars, but it is listed in one exchange. When you want to withdraw, you will be asked to deposit some bitcoins or complete some conditions.If the token is not listed on more than 10 exchanges and has good liquidity, it is better not to trust the value that appears to you, because it will most likely be fake.If I say now I have 10 bitcoins and I want to sell them, a lot will give you a value for them, but if I say I have 100 billion of X unlnown coin, no one will want that, big coin numbers does not create value.
